{"tid":987283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂喂喂唔好屌政府呀呢獲，大把連登醫護狗反對加學位","createTime":"2019-01-19T07:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T14:02:47.000Z","uid":223484,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e438fb11817128e231c60855e16aaac9831bec0","tid":987283,"uid":223484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/955977\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/955977</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登醫護狗論點： <br />\n<br />\n1. 人手無不足呀，係制度問題<br />\n<br />\n2. 供應多左都無用<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，一講到自己利益，理撚得實際人手情況，唔理病人，反對先"},{"pid":"fa783ae4afb892c2eba0a7b4cde76cfe8e5ff425","tid":987283,"uid":224510,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"實情想加人工啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4324147294e73440dc10f79cc4264074b2edf1","tid":987283,"uid":194415,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"加人工根本解決唔到呢事件<br />\n只有加人加學額<br />\n<br />\n不過呢，由於大陸要整死香港，香港政府又配合消滅自己<br />\n所以最後係唔會加學額<br />\n只會加入講普通話既醫護人員<br />\n<br />\n到大家老左，唔講普通話就等死冇人理啦"},{"pid":"7e1091bbbda0b24dae4e47e8aed2cf92788b882f","tid":987283,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"應該好快會引入支那醫護高才生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 發夢夢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2861faf342ab848ff10a6d659a56b05e3262bf75","tid":987283,"uid":85791,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"咁事實上人手真係冇不足 係醫管局唔請人 寧願加薪都唔請人<br />\n我諗做到狗咁嗰班醫護寧願涷薪都想請多個人<br />\n開三萬都留唔住d護士 再加都冇用 因為根本唔係錢既問題<br />\n係人手不足令醫療質素大降既問題(我明無論有幾忙都要維持水平 但呢個唔係有心同專業就做到 大家都係人)<br />\n每個人都有機會入醫院 呢d市民真係會受返<br />\n話護士想加人工嗰d到底係死蠢定係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea36f9197b4d1fd264845df9b39eebf453041fdf","tid":987283,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:41:40.000Z","msg":"加人工就解決到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8e05f81bc6180ee96747f0312ec45cade0df91","tid":987283,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"一早講撚左 <br />\n<br />\n醫管局本身就係 醫生護士話事既機構 <br />\n<br />\n搞到今日咁 , 班醫生護士怪乜撚個啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪又係佢地自己人既屎"},{"pid":"e48c2c0aada5657b2e08f5b0ebde9822c894e5ed","tid":987283,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"我踢爆班賤種反對引入英聯邦醫生一樣比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n連登醫護狗話加學位就會質素下降,以威脅病人安全威脅市民"},{"pid":"ce42a47c0fd261f039e146abecb16f09f0baba02","tid":987283,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"願意涷薪同想請多個人咪想自己做少d<br />\n叫市民有假唔放支持自己做少d.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如叫班友簽名求政府扣自己8千人工去請人"}]}